The arch mages of old knew the secrets of opening portals to other
dimansions. Long ago this knowledge was completely lost to the magic
community. Recently, some remnants of this knowlege were discovered
in a lost tome in the library in the circle. Thus far only a few 
locations are posible but with more expirimentation new locations may
be revealed.

Grimhaven, The Circle, Cloud city, The heart of the Volcano and Auria.
